Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(197.4,200.557)}{\fs25\c&H78BDE7&\fad(0,808)}24小时\N\N{\fs15}第三季  第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\move(189.6,121.6,193.8,105.6,0,356)}{\b1\bord0\shad3\3c&H2F2F2F&\4c&H336D99&}{\fs10}{\t(0,356,\fs20)}前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能拿到基勒的剧本呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What if I can get us a copy of keeler's playbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是"剧本"?\N{\r原文字幕}What exactly do you mean by "playbook"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚辩论的所有预稿\N{\r原文字幕}His entire prep for tonight's debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-见鬼 叫你别这么干  -听我说?\N{\r原文字幕}-Damn it, I told you to drop that.  -Will you just listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些内容你需要看一下\N{\r原文字幕}There is something you need to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么我需要看的\N{\r原文字幕}There's nothing I need to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于安妮的 我们所不知道的她\N{\r原文字幕}It's about anne. It's something that we didn't know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会毁掉我们大家\N{\r原文字幕}Something that could damage all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在能和你谈谈吗?  -当然\N{\r原文字幕}-Can I talk to you now?  -Yeah, Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金 什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}Kim, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯和我交往一段时间了\N{\r原文字幕}Chase and I have been going out for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是认真的\N{\r原文字幕}and it's starting to get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很在乎他 爸\N{\r原文字幕}I really care for him, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎么看?  -我不知道\N{\r原文字幕}-So what do you think?  -I don't know what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放拉姆·萨拉扎\N{\r原文字幕}We want the release of Ramon Salazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们拒绝\N{\r原文字幕}If you refuse to comply,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就散播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}the virus will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病毒被做成了晶体状\N{\r原文字幕}It looks like the virus was delivered in a crystalline form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许病毒就在白粉中\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe what you're looking for is a white powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如一包可卡因 或海洛因?\N{\r原文字幕}It would look like a bag of cocaine or heroin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 也许这是他们的诡计 毒贩以为自己在卖毒品\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, that may even be the strategy. Someone thinks they're selling a bag of coke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实则是在传播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}when, in fact, they're handling the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你哪儿来的钱  -这不重要\N{\r原文字幕}-Where did you get that money  -It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要这钱\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, we needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我弄到了钱\N{\r原文字幕}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样帮助家里人?\N{\r原文字幕}So this is how you're going to help you're family?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贩毒?\N{\r原文字幕}By dealing drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是贩毒 只是运送\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not dealing them. It's a stupid delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子带着一包有病毒的毒品倒处走\N{\r原文字幕}That kid's walking around with a bag of cocaine that's got the virus in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而毫不知情\N{\r原文字幕}He doesn't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到他 阻止毒品散播\N{\r原文字幕}I need to find him and stop him from putting it into circulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没注射毒品吧?\N{\r原文字幕}You didn't shoot up, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么? 你以为瞒得住我?\N{\r原文字幕}Why? You think you can hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想瞒你\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not trying to hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我是想戒掉  -戒掉还不够 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm trying to quit.  -Okay. People don't just quit, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想\N{\r原文字幕}I am not
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下毒瘾记录 懂吗?\N{\r原文字幕}going on record with this addiction. Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一知道此事的人 不要告诉别人\N{\r原文字幕}You're the only person who knows about it, so it's going to stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我最新情报\N{\r原文字幕}Give me an update.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔还在家里\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle's still in his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,货呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What about the package?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他手上\N{\r原文字幕}It's with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拉姆呢?  -等着回家呢\N{\r原文字幕}-And Ramon?  -Just waiting to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\r原文字幕}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚当 下载大家的会议文件夹了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Adam, have you downloaded everyone's folders for the meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没 我还在追踪病毒的详细资料\N{\r原文字幕}Not yet. I'm still pulling up some of the medical details about the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在那上面花太多时间\N{\r原文字幕}Don't waste a lot of time on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要知道症状出现24小时内会要人命\N{\r原文字幕}The only thing our people need to know is that it kills within 24 hours of exposure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有它正在凯尔 辛格勒手上\N{\r原文字幕}and we believe Kyle Singer is transporting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N{\r原文字幕}I got all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-找到辛格勒了吗?  -杰克要去找妮可·邓肯\N{\r原文字幕}-What about our approach to Singer?  -Jack's going to meet Nicole Duncan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶卫生局长\N{\r原文字幕}head of health services, Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会带防疫组去辛格勒家\N{\r原文字幕}They're going to take a haz-mat team over to Singer's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正在等她\N{\r原文字幕}He's waiting for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Hi, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很好 妮可 你呢?\N{\r原文字幕}I'm okay, Nicole. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午前还挺好\N{\r原文字幕}Until this afternoon, I was doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我...\N{\r原文字幕}You know, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说特里的事后 我联系过你\N{\r原文字幕}I tried to reach you after I heard about Teri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事之后 我是很消沉\N{\r原文字幕}After that, I kind of withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你打电话给我\N{\r原文字幕}But I appreciated the calls. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\N{\r原文字幕}We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚运行完马切尔的流行病估测分析程序\N{\r原文字幕}I just finished running Macer's epidemiological model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的估计不对\N{\r原文字幕}Her estimates were off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比先前预计的好还是坏?\N{\r原文字幕}Better or worse than we thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比以前坏两倍\N{\r原文字幕}Twice as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她估计一周后9%的人口会被感染\N{\r原文字幕}She had nine percent of the population infected within a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但几乎会达到20%\N{\r原文字幕}but it's closer to 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致死性比她预计的更高\N{\r原文字幕}And the infection-to-mortality rate is higher than her estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达到95%\N{\r原文字幕}Almost 95% lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我追踪细菌12年了 从没见过这样可怕的\N{\r原文字幕}I've been hunting germs for 12 years and I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\r原文字幕}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?\N{\r原文字幕}Are you feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 怎么了?\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在流汗\N{\r原文字幕}You're perspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我中午起就没休息过\N{\r原文字幕}I've been non-stop since noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我们还有8分钟时间\N{\r原文字幕}Look, we're going to be about eight minutes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到之前 你再翻翻防疫协约吧\N{\r原文字幕}It would be great if we could go over the quarantine protocols before we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -嗯\N{\r原文字幕}-No problem.  -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们拒绝 我们就散播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}If you refuse to comply, the virus will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,释放拉姆·萨拉扎...\N{\r原文字幕}I want the release of Ramon Salazar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖尔.\N{\r原文字幕}Gael
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这个\N{\r原文字幕}Here, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快查到电话的来源了\N{\r原文字幕}Closing in on the point of origin of this call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个伪造的编码了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}You see this code artifact here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯  -我有新发现\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah.  -I found a few more on this recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信它来自国内通信中转点\N{\r原文字幕}I think it's coming from a domestic switching node.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为电话是在美国境内打的?\N{\r原文字幕}You think the call was made from inside the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能 我把它传到你的系统\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe. I'm piping it over to your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你查一下有没有符合的\N{\r原文字幕}See if you can find a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -开完会再做吧\N{\r原文字幕}-Okay.  -But do it after the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么会?\N{\r原文字幕}What meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼会做些资源调动 以帮助杰克的行动\N{\r原文字幕}Tony's shifting resources to help Jack in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快找到病毒了\N{\r原文字幕}He's closing in on the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-盖尔  -嗯?\N{\r原文字幕}-Gael.  -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在杰克到辛格勒家前 把声音系统调整好\N{\r原文字幕}Jack needs that audio feed in place when he gets to Kyle Singer's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但托尼要我现在做些别的事\N{\r原文字幕}I know, but Tony needs me to take care of something right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-开完会我再帮你  -我需要你开会前做\N{\r原文字幕}-I'll get it to you after the meeting.  -I need you to do it before the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克正在路上 现在就去做\N{\r原文字幕}Jack's on his way there. So come do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 别烦我\N{\r原文字幕}I can't! Stop bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你的\N{\r原文字幕}I'll get it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\r原文字幕}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得拉姆回来后会怎样?\N{\r原文字幕}Have you thought about how it will be when Ramon comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样?\N{\r原文字幕}How it will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一样啊\N{\r原文字幕}Like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况不一样了 赫克托\N{\r原文字幕}Things have changed, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不一样\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他才走了三个月\N{\r原文字幕}He's only been gone three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不一样了\N{\r原文字幕}You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他进了监狱 你就是头儿\N{\r原文字幕}You've been in charge while he's been in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想这么轻易放弃?\N{\r原文字幕}Are you willing to give that up so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍尔就快截获我们的货了\N{\r原文字幕}Bauer's telling CTU he's about to intercept the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么会?  -不知道 我正在查\N{\r原文字幕}-How?  -I'm not sure. I'm about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-货还在凯尔 辛格勒手上?  -当然\N{\r原文字幕}-Is Gomez still on Kyle Singer?  -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\r原文字幕}Then we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 面试如何?\N{\r原文字幕}Hey, how was the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错\N{\r原文字幕}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 爸?\N{\r原文字幕}What's up, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈说你付清了\N{\r原文字幕}Your mother told me you paid the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们欠下的三个月房租\N{\r原文字幕}All three months we owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我赚了点钱\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. I came into a little money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个没工作的19岁男孩怎么赚钱?\N{\r原文字幕}How does a 19-year-old kid who doesn't have a job come into a little money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆和我 前天去赌马\N{\r原文字幕}Tim and I, we went down to the track the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在马厩有内线\N{\r原文字幕}He knows this guy over at the stables, so, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以我们赚了一笔  -你从哪儿来的钱?\N{\r原文字幕}-we got a tip.  -Where did you get the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 这很重要吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实话 付了三个月房租\N{\r原文字幕}Honestly, the rent's paid for three months. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在没压力了\N{\r原文字幕}The pressure's off us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干了非法的勾当?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you do something illegal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\r原文字幕}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去了圣阿尼塔\N{\r原文字幕}I told you we went to Santa Anita,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们运气好 我没干非法的事\N{\r原文字幕}and we got lucky. I didn't do anything illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别撒谎 我操的心已经够多了\N{\r原文字幕}Don't lie to me. I've got enough to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是当家的\N{\r原文字幕}Now, this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我付房租! 我照顾你和你妈妈\N{\r原文字幕}I pay the rent! I take care of you and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你找到工作\N{\r原文字幕}And when you get that job,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再来当家 还我的钱 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}you go ahead and pay me back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别走 我们还没谈完!\N{\r原文字幕}Wait a second. We're not done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谈完了\N{\r原文字幕}No, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑!\N{\r原文字幕}Don't walk away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该谢谢我 而不是在这里指责我\N{\r原文字幕}You should be thanking me instead of crawling up my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔!\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门!\N{\r原文字幕}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫凯尔 辛格勒\N{\r原文字幕}His name's Kyle Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为他正在转运病毒\N{\r原文字幕}We think he's transporting the virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他并不知道自己手上真正是什么\N{\r原文字幕}although it's likely he doesn't realize what he's carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会不知道?\N{\r原文字幕}How could he not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫生部相信 病毒被做成海洛因或可卡因的样子\N{\r原文字幕}Health Services believes that the virus was made to look like heroin or cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们了解到凯尔 辛格勒受雇 将毒品从墨西哥带给洛杉矶一毒贩\N{\r原文字幕}We know that Kyle Singer was hired to deliver a package from Mexico to a dealer in LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为自己在走私毒品\N{\r原文字幕}He thinks he's smuggling drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是他们的诡计\N{\r原文字幕}That's the working theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的问题是 辛格勒送交了毒品后\N{\r原文字幕}Now, here's the thing. Once Singer delivers that bag of powder,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病毒会被打开 然后在城市中传播\N{\r原文字幕}it gets cut up and distributed throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 一切就失控了\N{\r原文字幕}At that point, it becomes impossible to contain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶警局抓住辛格勒了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Was LAPD grabbing Singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\r原文字幕}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 他们就不能再快点吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Why not? Can't they get there faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉矶警局并不知晓 如何处理防疫区\N{\r原文字幕}LAPD is not trained to handle haz-zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克·鲍尔会和一组卫生部的人一起去\N{\r原文字幕}Jack Bauer's going to go in with a team from Health Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里进行协助\N{\r原文字幕}We're going to run the operation from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并及时通知总统\N{\r原文字幕}updating the president in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N{\r原文字幕}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得小心地接近辛格勒\N{\r原文字幕}we have to approach Singer with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他并不知道那包粉有多可怕\N{\r原文字幕}He has no idea how deadly this powder is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没骂他 只是问了他些问题\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not fighting. I'm just asking the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他应该尊重我们  -是的...\N{\r原文字幕}-He should respect us.  -Of course he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静一下吧?\N{\r原文字幕}now will you please calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1千8百美元...\N{\r原文字幕}$1,800 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说赌马赢的钱?\N{\r原文字幕}He said he won the money at the track?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是说谎不打草稿\N{\r原文字幕}He could come up with a better lie than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他说的是真的\N{\r原文字幕}Well, maybe he's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧 海伦\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, come on, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你去哪儿?  -随便\N{\r原文字幕}-Where you going?  -Wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包里是什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What's in the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-衣服  -打开看下\N{\r原文字幕}-Some clothes.  -Well, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把包打开\N{\r原文字幕}Open the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告你: 把包打开\N{\r原文字幕}I'm warning you: Open that bag
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我自己来\N{\r原文字幕}or I'm going to open it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈?\N{\r原文字幕}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-凯尔 听爸的话  -这不关他的事\N{\r原文字幕}-Kyle, listen to your father.  -It's none of his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家 就得听我的!\N{\r原文字幕}As long as you're living in my house, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家?\N{\r原文字幕}Your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你家 你连房租都付不起\N{\r原文字幕}This isn't your house. You can't even pay the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别 凯尔...\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, Kyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 这是我的隐私 求你了?\N{\r原文字幕}Come on, will you quit snooping, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想都别想\N{\r原文字幕}Don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么? 嗯?\N{\r原文字幕}What is this? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可卡因? 海洛因?\N{\r原文字幕}Coke? Heroin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还给我 爸  -你说什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-Give it back, dad.  -What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要它  -"需要"是什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}-I need it.  -What do you mean, you "need" it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吸毒?\N{\r原文字幕}What are you, some kind of junkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\r原文字幕}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把它交给某个人? 如果没办到的话...\N{\r原文字幕}I'm just delivering it to this guy, okay? And if I don't get it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁?\N{\r原文字幕}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-某个人而已?  -他是谁?!\N{\r原文字幕}-It's just a guy, okay?  -Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫什么名字\N{\r原文字幕}Give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔 回答你爸\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle, answer your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 好吗?!\N{\r原文字幕}You just give it to me, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样! 别这样 你们两个!\N{\r原文字幕}Stop it! Hey, stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩! 别这样!\N{\r原文字幕}Both of you! Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手! 山姆! 住手 山姆!\N{\r原文字幕}Stop! Sam! Sam, don't, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔!\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一遍\N{\r原文字幕}I can't reiterate this enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是场真正的威胁\N{\r原文字幕}This is a credible threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不快一步 萨拉扎的人就会散播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}Salazar's people will release this virus if we don't find it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家开工吧\N{\r原文字幕}So lets get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要一间绝尘室 有摄相和收音系统\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, we're going to need a white room with full audio and video capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好后通知我\N{\r原文字幕}Get me 3b if that's available.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让疑犯签字 我马上过去\N{\r原文字幕}Log him in. I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是应该和我爸在一起吗\N{\r原文字幕}I thought you were supposed to be with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来是 但他派我回来\N{\r原文字幕}I was. He sent me back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\r原文字幕}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,审问帕克\N{\r原文字幕}To question Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕克? 他已经供出了凯尔 辛格勒 还有什么好问的?\N{\r原文字幕}Parker? He already turned in Kyle Singer. What else are you going to get from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是问题所在\N{\r原文字幕}And that's the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不明白  -你爸让我坐冷板凳 金\N{\r原文字幕}-I don't understand. -Your dad's sidelining me, Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不让我参与行动\N{\r原文字幕}He's making me sit out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\r原文字幕}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢?\N{\r原文字幕}Why do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我俩的关系?\N{\r原文字幕}Because of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-蔡斯 抱歉...  -他说他在保护我...\N{\r原文字幕}-Chase, I'm sorry...  -He says he's protecting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是需要他保护的人\N{\r原文字幕}but I'm not the one he's trying to protect here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在怪我?\N{\r原文字幕}You're not blaming me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 我们还不该告诉他\N{\r原文字幕}Look, all I'm saying is, we shouldn't have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们该怎么办?\N{\r原文字幕}What were we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直地下情 直到被人发现?\N{\r原文字幕}Keep sneaking around until someone catches us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以再等等\N{\r原文字幕}We could have waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到什么时候?\N{\r原文字幕}Until when?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么时候告诉他 都是一样的结果\N{\r原文字幕}He'd have the same response no matter when we told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去审帕克这小子了\N{\r原文字幕}I got to deal with this kid Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰弗里\N{\r原文字幕}Jeffery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的饭烂透了\N{\r原文字幕}The food's exceptionally bad today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家哪条法律规定\N{\r原文字幕}Aren't there laws in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用残忍和不人道的惩罚?\N{\r原文字幕}for cruel and unusual punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉安尼康 我有话要说\N{\r原文字幕}Tell Annicon, I'm ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲍尔没告诉我 但萨拉扎确实有些手段\N{\r原文字幕}Bauer couldn't tell me, but Salazar's got some kind of leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让他得到释放\N{\r原文字幕}Enough to get him released.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让这杂种 浪费我两年的努力\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not about to let this son of a bitch erase the last two years of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打给你在国防部的朋友 看能得到什么消息\N{\r原文字幕}Call your friend at the state department, see what he can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是安尼康\N{\r原文字幕}Annicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-安尼康先生?  -嗯\N{\r原文字幕}-Mr. Annicon?  -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰夫•本森 是萨拉扎的看守\N{\r原文字幕}This is Jeff Benson, Salazar's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你\N{\r原文字幕}I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 萨拉扎要见你\N{\r原文字幕}Sir, Salazar asked to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\r原文字幕}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有话要跟你说\N{\r原文字幕}He says he's ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来\N{\r原文字幕}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别问我原因 照办就行\N{\r原文字幕}Don't ask me why, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:14:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能拿到退款\N{\r原文字幕}I hope you can get a refund.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退款?\N{\r原文字幕}A refund?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让卖这份垃圾给你的人退款\N{\r原文字幕}From whoever sold you that load of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫,\N{\r原文字幕}David
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基勒会用这个在辩论中攻击你\N{\r原文字幕}Keeler is going to use this against you in this debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无视它对你没有任何好处\N{\r原文字幕}Now, ignoring it's not going to make it go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出回应也不会显得更高贵\N{\r原文字幕}Neither will dignifying it with a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会指出安妮曾经做过伪证 别忘了\N{\r原文字幕}He's going to claim that Anne perjured herself, which, in case you've forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-做伪证是大罪  -安妮没犯罪\N{\r原文字幕}-is a felony.  -Anne is no felon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这句话足以毁了你\N{\r原文字幕}The allegation itself is enough to damage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大卫 请想一想\N{\r原文字幕}Now, come on, David please, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道要参加这辩论 不能不做回应\N{\r原文字幕}You know you can't go into this debate without some kind of response.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么办?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you propose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和安妮谈谈\N{\r原文字幕}Talk to Anne,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她告诉你一切\N{\r原文字幕}make sure she's told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已经告诉我一切了\N{\r原文字幕}She has told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和安妮交往以来\N{\r原文字幕}Ever since I started seeing Anne,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老是抓住机会 破坏我们的关系\N{\r原文字幕}you've taken every chance to undermine our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-因为你不喜欢她...  -是的 我不喜欢她\N{\r原文字幕}-Just because you don't like her...  -You're absolutely right, I don't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我和安妮之间的事 是你和安妮的事\N{\r原文字幕}This isn't about me and Anne. It's about you and Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她没有隐瞒任何事 那很好 她也不必隐瞒\N{\r原文字幕}Now, if she's got nothing to hide, fine, David, she's got nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:16:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得在与基勒的电视辩论前 查清楚\N{\r原文字幕}But you'd better find out before you face off with Keeler on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问过你朋友杰克·鲍尔发生什么事了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you ask your friend Jack Bauer what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问了 是吗?\N{\r原文字幕}You did, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他不会说\N{\r原文字幕}But he wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不爽吧 路易斯 被蒙在鼓里\N{\r原文字幕}Must be very frustrating, Luis, being kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么要说的?\N{\r原文字幕}You have something to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你还没回答我?  -有屁快放\N{\r原文字幕}-I asked you here, didn't I?  -Then start talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小时前 我的耐性就用光了\N{\r原文字幕}because you used up my patience an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是只叨着骨头的狗 路易斯\N{\r原文字幕}you are dog with a bone, Luis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦咬住了 就不肯放\N{\r原文字幕}Once you bite down, you don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去后\N{\r原文字幕}When I'm out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望看见你又咬住我\N{\r原文字幕}I don't want you on me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候出去?\N{\r原文字幕}When you're out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问得好\N{\r原文字幕}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几小时后 我就能回家了\N{\r原文字幕}In a few hours, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?\N{\r原文字幕}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做到的?\N{\r原文字幕}And how will you manage that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫克托是个好兄弟\N{\r原文字幕}Hector's a good brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他有监狱的钥匙\N{\r原文字幕}Unless he's got a key to this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-否则你哪都别想去  -他就是有钥匙\N{\r原文字幕}-you're not going anywhere.  -But he does have a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他拧动钥匙\N{\r原文字幕}And when he turns it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这两年的时间\N{\r原文字幕}the last two years of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽自己家人的时间\N{\r原文字幕}all the hours you've spent away from your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了抓我所做的一切努力\N{\r原文字幕}all the work you've done to put me in here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会白费...\N{\r原文字幕}will go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... 像这样\N{\r原文字幕}... just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想说这些给你听 路易斯\N{\r原文字幕}I wanted you to hear it from me, Luis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这会是你最后听到的话\N{\r原文字幕}I wanted it to be the last thing you ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就能见到你儿子了\N{\r原文字幕}Your son will be returned to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得凯尔肯定有问题\N{\r原文字幕}I'm just saying that Kyle is in over his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不用请律师\N{\r原文字幕}We're not calling a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他还没被捕  -暂时没有\N{\r原文字幕}-He hasn't even been arrested.  -Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他不会被捕\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe he won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不要管这事\N{\r原文字幕}If we leave it alone, don't do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情可能很快就会结束了\N{\r原文字幕}maybe this whole thing will just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你不认真的吧  -我是认真的 山姆?\N{\r原文字幕}-You can't be serious.  -Why not, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要搞得人尽皆知?\N{\r原文字幕}Why do we have to let anybody know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-因为这是违法的  -那你要我怎么做\N{\r原文字幕}-Because it's against the law not to.  -What are you suggesting we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫警察?\N{\r原文字幕}call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再用举报奖金付房租\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe they'll give us a reward and then we can pay our rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样做\N{\r原文字幕}All right, that wasn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\r原文字幕}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊!\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在干嘛?  -甩掉这玩意儿!\N{\r原文字幕}-Hey, what are you doing?  -I'm going to get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要送儿子进监狱?!  -等待\N{\r原文字幕}-You want to visit your son in jail?!  -Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海伦!\N{\r原文字幕}Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-后退! 后退!  -你们是什么人?\N{\r原文字幕}-Get back! Get back!  -Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔 辛格勒在哪儿?!\N{\r原文字幕}Where's Kyle Singer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-凯尔 辛格勒!  -他不在\N{\r原文字幕}-Kyle Singer!  -He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他隔离 做全面血检 拿棉签来\N{\r原文字幕}Isolate him and draw blood for a full panel. Get an oral swab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封死所有窗户和通风口\N{\r原文字幕}Seal off all these windows and vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!\N{\r原文字幕}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿! 在这儿!\N{\r原文字幕}In here! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不!  -隔离她\N{\r原文字幕}-No!  -Put her in quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 病毒散出去了\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, the virus is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复 病毒散出去了\N{\r原文字幕}I repeat, the virus is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 杰克 在哪儿?\N{\r原文字幕}Copy that, Jack. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,污水处理系统\N{\r原文字幕}In the sewage system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知污水局关闭底下水系统\N{\r原文字幕}Get DWP to shut down the lines from ground zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能散播到空气中了\N{\r原文字幕}It might also be airborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让消防局和警局安设隔离墙\N{\r原文字幕}Get the fire department and LAPD to set up a perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知他们这里是三级疫区\N{\r原文字幕}Tell them we've got a level-three hot zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\r原文字幕}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进\N{\r原文字幕}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦恩说你想见我\N{\r原文字幕}Wayne said you wanted to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基勒.\N{\r原文字幕}Keeler
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会在辩论中提及你前夫\N{\r原文字幕}He's bringing your ex-husband into this debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证监会对他公司的调查\N{\r原文字幕}The SEC's investigation into his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 泰德被判有罪 正在服刑\N{\r原文字幕}Well, Ted was convicted, and served his sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的\N{\r原文字幕}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉过我的\N{\r原文字幕}I know what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把所有的事都告诉你了\N{\r原文字幕}I told you everything there is to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德的公司引进了一种高血压药...\N{\r原文字幕}Ted's company was introducing a hypertension drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你审过检验报告  -对\N{\r原文字幕}-and you reviewed the research.  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果证实报告是捏造的\N{\r原文字幕}Which later turned out to have been fabricated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德知道是假的\N{\r原文字幕}Which Ted knew at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道\N{\r原文字幕}and I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在泰德又称你也知道\N{\r原文字幕}Now Ted's claiming that you both knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能推翻自己8年前的证词\N{\r原文字幕}He can't reverse himself 8 years after giving sworn testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做了\N{\r原文字幕}Well, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会在记者会上公开说明\N{\r原文字幕}And he's willing to go on record with the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能说 他在说谎\N{\r原文字幕}I don't know what to say, except he's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的和他的不一致\N{\r原文字幕}It's your word against his.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫...\N{\r原文字幕}David...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有理由怀疑我\N{\r原文字幕}you have reason to be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝明白\N{\r原文字幕}God knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾被最信任的人被叛过\N{\r原文字幕}you've been betrayed by some of the people you've trusted most,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是雪莉\N{\r原文字幕}but I'm not Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实我已说过一次\N{\r原文字幕}I told you the whole truth once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会过多解释\N{\r原文字幕}I'm not going to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为没什么比你我之间的信任更重要...\N{\r原文字幕}Because if there's anything less than complete trust between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你 安妮\N{\r原文字幕}I do trust you, Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该相信我\N{\r原文字幕}You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\r原文字幕}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈 大卫 我和安妮正在谈\N{\r原文字幕}We need to talk, David. I'm with Anne now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜她全盘否认了\N{\r原文字幕}Ah, let me guess she denied everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信她\N{\r原文字幕}I believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我有办法处理这些事\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, well, listen, I might be able to make this whole thing go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做?\N{\r原文字幕}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,礼堂见面再谈...\N{\r原文字幕}Meet you in the auditorium...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单独\N{\r原文字幕}alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\r原文字幕}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有时间看妮可写的行动报告了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}So have you had a chance to take a look at Nicole's field report yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 快看完了\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么看法?\N{\r原文字幕}What are your impressions?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从我读到的内容看 比较乐观\N{\r原文字幕}Based on what I've read so far, I'm optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们能够控制病毒?\N{\r原文字幕}So you think we'll be able to contain the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以控制受害者人数\N{\r原文字幕}At the very least, we should be able to limit the casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但病毒散布到空中了啊?\N{\r原文字幕}Even though the virus was airborne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有传播的危险 但妮可的小组反应迅速\N{\r原文字幕}Well, there is some risk of it spreading, but Nicole's team acted fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们疏散并封锁了那栋楼 并隔离了辛格勒一家\N{\r原文字幕}They evacuated and sealed off the apartment building and quarantined the Singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.92,0:22:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么时候出化验结果?  -5分钟 最多10分钟\N{\r原文字幕}-When do we get the test results?  -Five minutes, ten tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来运气不错啊?\N{\r原文字幕}So looks like we lucked out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是该有点运气  -很好 听着\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah, we deserve a little luck.  -All right, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要挂了 有消息随时通知我 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}I got to go. Make sure you keep me in the loop, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 你也一样  -好的\N{\r原文字幕}-Okay, you do the Same.  -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 警局已经设了隔离区 他们要知道刚才15分钟的风向\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, LAPD's setting up the perimeter, but they need wind vectors for the last 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打给气象局\N{\r原文字幕}Call meteorology.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,212号分机\N{\r原文字幕}Extension 212.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 媒体知道了被抛在卫生部外的\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, local news picked up the story about the dead body
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那具尸体\N{\r原文字幕}being dumped at Health Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\r原文字幕}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要听解释 我该怎么说?\N{\r原文字幕}They want a statement. What do you want me to tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥都别说\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 有个叫典狱官 米切尔的打电话找你\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, Warden Mitchell is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从监狱打来 说是急事\N{\r原文字幕}He's calling from the prison. He says it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿尔梅达\N{\r原文字幕}Almeida.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛格勒先生 辛格勒夫人?\N{\r原文字幕}Mr. and Mrs. Singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒底出了什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟毒品又没关系\N{\r原文字幕}Because this is not about drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可能感染了一种病毒\N{\r原文字幕}We think you've been exposed to a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-病毒?  -叫做科迪勒拉病毒\N{\r原文字幕}-A virus?  -It's called Cordillera Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们儿子今早偷将病毒 从墨西哥携带入境\N{\r原文字幕}We believe that your son carried it in from Mexico this morning without knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"携带"怎么讲? 怎么会?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you mean "carried it in"? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为自己在运送毒品\N{\r原文字幕}He thought he was carrying drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被感染了?\N{\r原文字幕}So, we've been exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的\N{\r原文字幕}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么后果? 我们安全吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Wh... what does that mean? Are we sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检验结果出来前 你们将被隔离\N{\r原文字幕}We're going to have to keep you quarantined until we get the results back from your tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\r原文字幕}Excuse me for one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 我是鲍尔  -杰克 我是托尼\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah, this is Bauer.  -Jack, it's Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 我认为凯尔 辛格勒被感染了\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, I think Kyle Singer's been exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们已集中全力在他身上\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, we've already got an all points out on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们设好隔离区了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Have you set a perimeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正尽全力控制事态\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. We're doing everything we can to contain this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有探员和部门 组成了高度机密的智囊团队\N{\r原文字幕}All agencies and departments are in the loop on a need-to-know basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干得好  -杰克 听着\N{\r原文字幕}-Okay, good work.  -Listen, Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本不该现在告诉你 但\N{\r原文字幕}I know this isn't a best time to tell you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.90,0:24:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到坏消息 你一定想知道\N{\r原文字幕}I just got some bad news. I figured you'd want to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 安尼康被杀了\N{\r原文字幕}Luis Annicon was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-被杀 怎么会?  -萨拉扎的看守干的\N{\r原文字幕}-Murdered, how?  -Salazar's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们扣押了他 他说...\N{\r原文字幕}We've got him in custody. He claims that ...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉扎绑架了他儿子 如果不这样做就撕票\N{\r原文字幕}Salazar had a son kidnapped and threatened to kill him if he didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 很抱歉 我知道你俩为了查案曾紧密合作\N{\r原文字幕}Jack, I'm sorry. I know you two worked closely on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.03,0:24:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-托尼 我马上回来  -没事吧?\N{\r原文字幕}-Tony, I'm going to have to get back to you.  -Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.54,0:24:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我马上回来  -杰克?\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm going to get back to you.  -Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-结果不对吧  -是对的\N{\r原文字幕}-These results can't be right.  -They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再查一次  -查过了\N{\r原文字幕}-Check it again.  -I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血液和唾液 空气和体表 都呈阴性\N{\r原文字幕}Blood and saliva, atmospheric and surface tests, they're all negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.17,0:25:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点病毒的痕迹都没发现\N{\r原文字幕}We can't find even a... a trace amount of this virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.37,0:25:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛? 你还没冲洗消毒呢\N{\r原文字幕}What the hell are you doing? You haven't showered down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.16,0:25:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没危险了  -什么?\N{\r原文字幕}-We're not at risk.  -What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.70,0:25:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我看到粉末飘出来  -它是无害的 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}-I watched the powder get out.  -It's harmless, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.83,0:25:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呈硅酸盐状 仅此而已\N{\r原文字幕}Some form of silicate, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.11,0:25:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-啊?  -白粉中没有病毒\N{\r原文字幕}-What?  -There is no virus in the powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.39,0:25:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们检验了五份样本 一点痕量都没有\N{\r原文字幕}We tested five Samples. There weren't even trace amounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.16,0:25:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空气和体表分析都呈阴性\N{\r原文字幕}Atmospheric and surface analysis also came up negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.29,0:25:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔父母也呈阴性\N{\r原文字幕}and Kyle's parents tested negative, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定?\N{\r原文字幕}You're sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.25,0:25:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一不确定的是 我们是否找到了正确线索\N{\r原文字幕}The only thing I'm not sure about is if we're on the right trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.72,0:25:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 抛在卫生部外的尸体与凯尔 辛格勒有关\N{\r原文字幕}No. No, the body that was dropped off at Health Services was linked to Kyle Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉扎怎么可能付钱让他运送 一包没用的白粉?\N{\r原文字幕}Why would Salazar's people pay him to bring across a bag of worthless powder?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.00,0:25:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 那我们该从何处着手?\N{\r原文字幕}Fine, Jack, but where do we even start looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.41,0:25:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\r原文字幕}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\r原文字幕}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:26:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马切尔说毒品只可能以晶体形态被运送 是吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Macer said the only way to transport the virus was in crystalline form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.82,0:26:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 这是病毒离开人体 唯一能存活的形态\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, that's the only way it can survive outside a living body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.90,0:26:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许病毒根本没有离开人体呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What if it was never outside a living body?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.94,0:26:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.93,0:26:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是病毒被携带在活人身上呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What if the virus was transported in a living host?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.02,0:26:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是凯尔 辛格勒今早离开墨西哥前就被感染了呢?\N{\r原文字幕}What if Kyle Singer was infected earlier this morning in Mexico before he even left?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.42,0:26:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但萨拉扎无法左右辛格勒的行动 到处传染人呢\N{\r原文字幕}But Salazar has no leverage if Singer was walking around, infecting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.17,0:26:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题就在这 他还没有传染性\N{\r原文字幕}That's the point. He wouldn't be contagious yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.61,0:26:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜伏期有14小时\N{\r原文字幕}The incubation period is 14 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.39,0:26:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 想一想\N{\r原文字幕}Right. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.09,0:26:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道凯尔 辛格勒 11小时前在墨西哥\N{\r原文字幕}We know for a fact that Kyle Singer was in Mexico 11 hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.49,0:26:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫克托 萨拉扎威胁3小时后散播病毒\N{\r原文字幕}Hector Salazar hasn't threatened to release the virus for another three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.87,0:26:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加起来正好\N{\r原文字幕}The math adds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找到凯尔 辛格勒\N{\r原文字幕}We need to find Kyle Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.63,0:26:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂?  -琳达.\N{\r原文字幕}-Hello?  -Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔 我们没什么好说的了\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle, I told you, I have nothing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.25,0:26:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 听我说 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}No, listen to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.05,0:26:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我有麻烦  -当然 因为你在做毒品交易\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm in trouble.  -Yeah, because you're dealing drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.58,0:26:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你帮忙\N{\r原文字幕}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.26,0:26:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了?\N{\r原文字幕}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.26,0:26:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸发现了白粉\N{\r原文字幕}My dad found the stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.32,0:26:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大吵一架\N{\r原文字幕}We got in a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们发生了争抢 货被我爸抢去了\N{\r原文字幕}I split, but he's still got it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.05,0:26:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得把货交给那些人 懂吗?\N{\r原文字幕}And I got to get this them, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.32,0:26:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人可不好对付 我得把事情搞定\N{\r原文字幕}These guys are hard core. I got to make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.39,0:26:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定? 怎么做?\N{\r原文字幕}Make it right? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.46,0:26:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想 也许\N{\r原文字幕}I know, I was thinking, you know, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:26:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还钱给他们 也许\N{\r原文字幕}maybe I could pay them enough, you know, just
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.55,0:27:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们就不再骚扰我  -你想让我给你钱?\N{\r原文字幕}-to keep them off my back. -You want me to give you money?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 只是借\N{\r原文字幕}No, no, no, just borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.43,0:27:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借多少?\N{\r原文字幕}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.41,0:27:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两万美元 我在街上\N{\r原文字幕}It's about 20 grand on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.94,0:27:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没那么多钱 凯尔\N{\r原文字幕}I don't have that kind of money, Kyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.72,0:27:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说你爸在家有些现金吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Didn't you say your dad keeps some cash around the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.17,0:27:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没那么多  -琳达 听我说!\N{\r原文字幕}-Not that much.  -Linda, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.52,0:27:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人...\N{\r原文字幕}These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.30,0:27:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拿不出东西 他们会杀了我\N{\r原文字幕}they will kill me if I don't give them something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了... 多少帮点忙\N{\r原文字幕}Please... please, anything will help right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.60,0:27:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我也卷进去?\N{\r原文字幕}Now you want me to get involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.80,0:27:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就... 求你借点给我 多少都行\N{\r原文字幕}Just... please let me borrow something, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.11,0:27:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会还你的 我发誓\N{\r原文字幕}I'll pay you back, I swear to god.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.09,0:27:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在哪儿?  -商场外\N{\r原文字幕}-Where are you?  -I'm at the mall.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我尽快过去  -谢谢\N{\r原文字幕}-I'll get there as soon as I can.  -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.17,0:27:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反恐局已知道白粉只是幌子 他们正在找辛格勒\N{\r原文字幕}CTU knows the powder is not real. Now they're going after Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.25,0:27:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我怎么做?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.56,0:27:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着他 没人的时候\N{\r原文字幕}Stay with him, and as soon as he's alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.61,0:27:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-抓住他控制他  -是\N{\r原文字幕}-Grab him and take him into containment.  -Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.40,0:27:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让警察捉住他\N{\r原文字幕}You can't let the cops get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.51,0:27:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有辛格勒 就没用了\N{\r原文字幕}We need Singer to make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然释放萨拉扎是不可能的\N{\r原文字幕}Of course there's no way we'll ever release Salazar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.70,0:28:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反恐局很快就能掌控局面\N{\r原文字幕}CTU is very close to containing the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.33,0:28:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对\N{\r原文字幕}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.95,0:28:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 斯坦\N{\r原文字幕}All right, Stan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有消息我会通知你\N{\r原文字幕}I'll make sure you're kept in the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.33,0:28:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有新情况吗 韦恩?\N{\r原文字幕}What have we got, Wayne?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.48,0:28:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同安妮的前夫谈过了\N{\r原文字幕}I just talked to Anne's ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.65,0:28:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 泰德 帕卡德想要的只是钱\N{\r原文字幕}Now, listen, all Ted Packard wants is money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.75,0:28:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们肯付钱 他就撤消陈述\N{\r原文字幕}If we pay him off, he'll recant before this debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是敲诈\N{\r原文字幕}That's blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.11,0:28:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是交易  -我不觉得\N{\r原文字幕}-That's business.  -I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.63,0:28:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫 比起去反驳对你不利的陈述\N{\r原文字幕}David, it's a hell of a lot cheaper than trying to defend against this allegation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.96,0:28:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可要便宜得多\N{\r原文字幕}which is going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勇于面对这些谎言\N{\r原文字幕}I've faced down worse lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的公信度还可以\N{\r原文字幕}I think I've earned some credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.26,0:28:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了今早的民意调查没有?\N{\r原文字幕}You read the polls this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.27,0:28:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基勒的支持率 逼近我们\N{\r原文字幕}Because Keeler is closing the gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.82,0:29:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竞选又提前了\N{\r原文字幕}and this race is much closer than it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.06,0:29:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 虽然这事令人不快 但\N{\r原文字幕}And listen, I know it's distasteful there, but
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.07,0:29:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以成本角度上 非常划算\N{\r原文字幕}in cost-benefit terms, it's a no brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮不会这样以为\N{\r原文字幕}Anne won't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-安妮不用知道  -我不会对她隐瞒\N{\r原文字幕}-Anne doesn't have to know.  -I can't keep it from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.12,0:29:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 这是你选的\N{\r原文字幕}Well, that's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.47,0:29:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事抖了出来\N{\r原文字幕}But if this comes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.19,0:29:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安妮就要上全国各大报纸的头条\N{\r原文字幕}Anne is going to find herself on the front page of every single newspaper in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.56,0:29:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫 她不是雪莉 她经不起那样的审视\N{\r原文字幕}and David, she's not Sherry. She's not equipped to handle that kind of scrutiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.88,0:29:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也没办法保护她\N{\r原文字幕}and you will not be able to protect her from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.51,0:29:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在辩论和事件爆发之间\N{\r原文字幕}Now, between this debate
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.34,0:29:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有足够时间考虑你的选择\N{\r原文字幕}and the threat of this outbreak, you have enough on your plate to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.23,0:29:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别当殉道者\N{\r原文字幕}Don't be a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.55,0:29:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事化小 小事化了\N{\r原文字幕}Keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.81,0:29:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一小时内能弄到钱\N{\r原文字幕}We could have the money within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.63,0:30:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\r原文字幕}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.95,0:30:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\r原文字幕}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.01,0:30:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们脱下了隔离服 就是说我们安全了?\N{\r原文字幕}They don't have their suits on. What does that mean? Are we okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.26,0:30:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 白粉没有病毒\N{\r原文字幕}Yes. The powder was harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-感谢上帝...  -你无缘无故这样对待我们\N{\r原文字幕}-Oh, thank god...  -Then you put us through all this for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-把我们吓个半死  -辛格勒先生 我们还要找你儿子\N{\r原文字幕}-You scared the hell out of us.  -Mr. Singer, we still need to find your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.19,0:30:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有线索 能帮我们找到他?\N{\r原文字幕}Is there anything that you can tell us that would help?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛? 不是说白粉没有病毒了吗\N{\r原文字幕}Why? You just said the powder was harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.98,0:30:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你儿子今早在墨西哥 感染了病毒\N{\r原文字幕}We believe that your son was infected with the virus in Mexico earlier this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.86,0:30:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他回家前\N{\r原文字幕}before he came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.41,0:30:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他具有传染性前 我们只有3小时找他\N{\r原文字幕}We have three hours to find him before he becomes contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\r原文字幕}What are you saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.01,0:30:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们儿子会死?\N{\r原文字幕}that our son could die?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对 有可能  -噢 上帝\N{\r原文字幕}-Yes, that could happen.  -Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.53,0:30:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们很难过 对不起\N{\r原文字幕}I know how difficult this must be for you, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.67,0:30:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们必须找到他 马上\N{\r原文字幕}But we need to find your son, we need to find him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.56,0:30:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-打过他手机吗?  -嗯 打不通\N{\r原文字幕}-Have you tried his cell phone?  -Yes. The line's been disconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.72,0:30:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 等等\N{\r原文字幕}No, wait. Oh, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.10,0:31:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\r原文字幕}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.98,0:31:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他早上拿走了我的电话  -号码多少?\N{\r原文字幕}-He took my phone this morning.  -What's the number?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.51,0:31:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,818-555-0103.\N{\r原文字幕}818-555-0103
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.73,0:31:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\r原文字幕}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.83,0:31:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你俩中找个人给他说\N{\r原文字幕}I'm going to need one of you to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.27,0:31:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错\N{\r原文字幕}This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.11,0:31:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没照顾好这个家 我没资格跟他说\N{\r原文字幕}I never would have done any of this if I couldn't take care of my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.08,0:31:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -你知道 这是真的\N{\r原文字幕}-No.  -Yes. You know, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.29,0:31:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 我是杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, it's Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.46,0:31:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克 我已通知警局 他们正全境抓捕辛格勒\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, Jack, I just spoke to LAPD. They've got a priority APB on Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我们找到了他的联系电话\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, good. I think we've got a number on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.03,0:31:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\r原文字幕}All right, look,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.03,0:31:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上对号码进行跟踪\N{\r原文字幕}we'll thread the line through a tracing matrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.76,0:31:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 号码是818-555-0103\N{\r原文字幕}Okay. The number is 818-555-0103.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.90,0:31:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把此号的线路 转到我手机上\N{\r原文字幕}I want you to route the call back to my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.52,0:31:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\r原文字幕}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.52,0:31:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪此号码 并将线路转到杰克手机上\N{\r原文字幕}I want you to trace that number and reroute the call to Jack's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁来打电话\N{\r原文字幕}I'm going to need one of you to make the call now,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.07,0:31:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量拖延通话时间 以便我们追踪他\N{\r原文字幕}I need you to keep him on the line as long as possible so we can trace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.29,0:31:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该跟他说什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What am I supposed to tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.06,0:31:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实\N{\r原文字幕}The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.78,0:32:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 设好了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, you set?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.72,0:32:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就绪\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-琳达  -凯尔 我是爸爸\N{\r原文字幕}-Linda.  -Kyle, it's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.14,0:32:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.23,0:32:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈谈\N{\r原文字幕}We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你想谈什么\N{\r原文字幕}Look, I don't know what you want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.67,0:32:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌你 知道吗?\N{\r原文字幕}I already know how pissed off you are, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.32,0:32:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 嗯\N{\r原文字幕}Look, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你做了什么...\N{\r原文字幕}whatever you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是想帮助我和你妈\N{\r原文字幕}I know you were just trying to help out your mom and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.30,0:32:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 除非你肯把东西还给我\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah, well, look, unless you're willing to give back the stuff you took,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.68,0:32:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才能把事情搞定 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}I got to deal with the situation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.54,0:32:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔! 拜托别挂电话\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle! Please, don't hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.17,0:32:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托! 听我说\N{\r原文字幕}Please! Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.04,0:32:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\r原文字幕}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.91,0:32:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有重要的事告诉你 拜托\N{\r原文字幕}What I'm telling you is important. Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.44,0:32:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须回家一趟\N{\r原文字幕}you have to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.71,0:32:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 你声音怎么有点奇怪?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad, why do you sound different?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.81,0:32:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我告诉你的事\N{\r原文字幕}I need you to trust me on something I'm about to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.35,0:32:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.28,0:32:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能感染了病毒\N{\r原文字幕}You may have gotten a virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.71,0:32:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在墨西哥的时候\N{\r原文字幕}something you picked up in Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.30,0:33:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我去了墨西哥?\N{\r原文字幕}How'd you know I went to Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.26,0:33:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不重要\N{\r原文字幕}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.02,0:33:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你可能身染重疾\N{\r原文字幕}But you may be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.78,0:33:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的 你得去看医生\N{\r原文字幕}And if you are, then you need to get checked out by a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.57,0:33:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我不知你在说什么?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad, I don't know what you're talking about, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.75,0:33:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我很好  -我知道这听起来很疯狂\N{\r原文字幕}-But I feel fine.  -I know it sounds crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.04,0:33:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却是真的\N{\r原文字幕}but it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.58,0:33:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有人想帮助你\N{\r原文字幕}Now, there's e some people here who are trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.83,0:33:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-警察?  -不是\N{\r原文字幕}-Cops?  -No
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 跟踪到电话了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, have you got a lock on this trace?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.02,0:33:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这孩子快挂电话了  -还要多久?\N{\r原文字幕}-We're going to lose this kid.  -How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.22,0:33:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查了信号塔 在半径三英里范围内\N{\r原文字幕}I've got the cell tower, but it's covering a three-mile radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.02,0:33:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信\N{\r原文字幕}I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.84,0:33:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太矛盾了 刚在说你们爱我\N{\r原文字幕}This fight, one minute you tell me that you love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.23,0:33:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一秒又把我出卖给警察\N{\r原文字幕}the next minute, you're selling me out to some cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.62,0:33:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是警察 凯尔\N{\r原文字幕}They're not police, Kyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.73,0:33:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是在阻止病毒扩散\N{\r原文字幕}They're just trying to stop this virus before it becomes an outbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.82,0:33:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我说了感觉很好 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Dad, I already told you I feel fine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说你几小时后 会出现病症\N{\r原文字幕}They're saying that you're not going to start feeling sick for another few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.56,0:33:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但到那时 就太迟了  -托尼 锁定位置了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}-But by then, it's going to be too late.  -Tony, have you got a lock yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要多久?\N{\r原文字幕}How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.34,0:33:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十秒\N{\r原文字幕}10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.25,0:33:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我干嘛? 去自首?\N{\r原文字幕}What do you want me to do? You want me to turn myself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.40,0:33:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你可能病了\N{\r原文字幕}Because you may be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.13,0:33:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的 其它人也会被感染\N{\r原文字幕}And if you are, other people are going to get infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:33:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-托尼...  -查到了 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}-Tony...  -We got it, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.39,0:33:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在洛斯费利兹商场 佛蒙特和日落街之间\N{\r原文字幕}He's at the Los Feliz Mall, between Vermont and Sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.80,0:34:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他的照片发给商场保安\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, get his photograph over to mall security.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.46,0:34:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们别接近他\N{\r原文字幕}Tell them not to approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.09,0:34:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克,\N{\r原文字幕}Jack
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.09,0:34:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开车去那儿要20分钟 我10分钟内在那儿布置队伍\N{\r原文字幕}you're 20 minutes away by car, I can land a team there in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.07,0:34:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\r原文字幕}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.31,0:34:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 别派蔡斯\N{\r原文字幕}Tony, I don't want you taking Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么?  -照我说的做\N{\r原文字幕}-Why not?  -I just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.97,0:34:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们\N{\r原文字幕}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.50,0:34:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们抓到了他 就通知你们\N{\r原文字幕}We'll notify you as soon as we have him in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.44,0:34:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 帮帮他\N{\r原文字幕}Please, help our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.83,0:34:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会的\N{\r原文字幕}We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.39,0:34:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱恩.\N{\r原文字幕}O'Brian
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.49,0:34:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萝伊 不知你听见了吗 托尼要马上出动\N{\r原文字幕}Chloe, I'm not sure you've heard yet, But Tony's heading off site for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.44,0:34:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\r原文字幕}He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.29,0:34:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下来几小时由我负责\N{\r原文字幕}Yeah. I'm taking over for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.32,0:34:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -通知你那个部门的人\N{\r原文字幕}-Okay.  -Let people in your area know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -谢谢\N{\r原文字幕}-Okay, I will.  -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.89,0:34:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?\N{\r原文字幕}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.15,0:34:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是米歇尔 她会掌管反恐小组几小时\N{\r原文字幕}Michelle. She's taking over CTU for a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.37,0:34:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼呢?\N{\r原文字幕}Where's Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.73,0:34:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们找出了辛格勒所在处\N{\r原文字幕}They have a location on Singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.01,0:34:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克无法及时赶到 托尼就去了\N{\r原文字幕}Jack can't get there in time, so Tony's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.97,0:34:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 托尼又不是外勤组的\N{\r原文字幕}What? Tony's not field ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.90,0:34:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们已有所行动 但将你排除在外\N{\r原文字幕}Seems like they're really going out of their way to cut you out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了让杰克讨厌的事?\N{\r原文字幕}Did you do something to piss off Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.68,0:34:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 蔡斯 只会让事情更糟\N{\r原文字幕}Bad idea, Chase. You're just going to make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼...\N{\r原文字幕}Tony...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.50,0:35:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说找到了凯尔 辛格勒 是真的吗?\N{\r原文字幕}I just heard they found Kyle Singer. Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.43,0:35:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知 我会和杰克在那儿碰头\N{\r原文字幕}We'll see. I'm meeting Jack over there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 帕克审讯完毕 该招的都招了\N{\r原文字幕}Look, I'm done with this kid Parker. He's said all he's gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.44,0:35:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我想跟这案子  -好啦\N{\r原文字幕}-I want back on the case.  -Yeah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.33,0:35:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来处理 蔡斯 好吗?\N{\r原文字幕}we're handling it now, Chase, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.01,0:35:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是杰克不想我参与吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Because Jack doesn't want me there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.63,0:35:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说了排挤我的理由吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did he tell you why he's cutting me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.25,0:35:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣 他是你上级 这是他的命令\N{\r原文字幕}I don't really care. He's your boss, it's his call.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.77,0:35:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不公平\N{\r原文字幕}This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.35,0:35:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说是因为金吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Did he tell you this is because of Kim?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.03,0:35:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我们在交往 他要我为此付出代价\N{\r原文字幕}He found out we were seeing each other, and this is how he's going to make me pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.79,0:35:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留着跟杰克谈吧\N{\r原文字幕}Take it up with Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.15,0:36:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把线路留给托尼\N{\r原文字幕}Just want to keep the line open for Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.20,0:36:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给杰克·鲍尔留言\N{\r原文字幕}Leave a message for Jack Bauer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.26,0:36:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}Damn it, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.21,0:36:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯.\N{\r原文字幕}Chase
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.35,0:36:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔡斯.\N{\r原文字幕}Chase
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.28,0:37:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我爸很生气 但他会消气的\N{\r原文字幕}Look, I know my dad can be hard, but he will come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道?\N{\r原文字幕}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.24,0:37:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我了解他\N{\r原文字幕}Because I know my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你并没有你想的那么了解他\N{\r原文字幕}Maybe you don't know him as well as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思?\N{\r原文字幕}What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.17,0:37:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么\N{\r原文字幕}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.04,0:37:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 金\N{\r原文字幕}It's okay. Forget it, Kim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.17,0:37:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得我已经够烦了吗?\N{\r原文字幕}Don't you think I feel bad enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.34,0:37:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很烦\N{\r原文字幕}Because I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.67,0:37:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不应该告诉他\N{\r原文字幕}We shouldn't have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.37,0:37:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有另外一个办法 就是停止交往\N{\r原文字幕}Well, the only other option I can think of is for us to stop seeing each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.86,0:37:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这不在我考虑范围内\N{\r原文字幕}which as far as I'm concerned, is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.41,0:37:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我应该考虑?\N{\r原文字幕}Or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.13,0:37:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-蔡斯 你有什么想法?  -我想做回我的工作\N{\r原文字幕}-Chase, what do you want?  -I want to be able to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.94,0:37:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金 快回工作岗位 托尼要到了\N{\r原文字幕}Kim, we need you at your station. Tony's about to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.90,0:38:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼·阿尔梅达 反恐小组\N{\r原文字幕}Tony Almeida, CTU.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.17,0:38:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到了你们要的人\N{\r原文字幕}I think we found the guy you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.97,0:38:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在大厅\N{\r原文字幕}He's in the rotunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.52,0:38:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-布朗森 看住东出口  -是\N{\r原文字幕}-Bronson, lock down the east exit.  -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.26,0:38:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮尔森 你去保安办公室\N{\r原文字幕}Pierson, I want you to run point from the security office.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.79,0:38:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\r原文字幕}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吸毒多久了 杰克?\N{\r原文字幕}How long have you been using, Jack?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.83,0:38:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\r原文字幕}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.11,0:38:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做过康复培训 能辨别出吸毒的人\N{\r原文字幕}I did a rotation in rehab. You learn to pick out when someone's using.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.31,0:38:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不知道你在说什么  -你知道\N{\r原文字幕}-I don't know what you're talking about.  -You know exactly what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.16,0:39:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多久了?\N{\r原文字幕}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一阵了\N{\r原文字幕}For a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.12,0:39:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样做才能瞒过萨拉扎\N{\r原文字幕}It was the only way I could maintain my cover with the Salazars.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.90,0:39:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-现在很兴奋?  -不\N{\r原文字幕}-Are you high now?  -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.95,0:39:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这个空了 杰克  -妮可 我没事\N{\r原文字幕}-It's empty, Jack.  -Nicole, I told you I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.86,0:39:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我看未必  -那你去打我的报告啊\N{\r原文字幕}-I'm not so sure.  -If you're not so sure, then turn me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.28,0:39:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想打你的报告 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}I don't want to turn you in, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心你\N{\r原文字幕}I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.20,0:39:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我已经戒了\N{\r原文字幕}You don't have to be. I've kicked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.66,0:39:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有责任控制病毒\N{\r原文字幕}I have a responsibility to stop this virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.72,0:39:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你这些阻碍 我相信你能发挥更大作用\N{\r原文字幕}and I am taking a calculated risk that you are more of an asset than a liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.47,0:39:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把事情搞砸了\N{\r原文字幕}Just please don't screw this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.94,0:39:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的\N{\r原文字幕}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.44,0:39:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂?  -喂 杰克\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah?  -Hey, Jack,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.73,0:40:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保安发现了辛格勒 我马上去逮捕他\N{\r原文字幕}Security found Singer. I'm about to pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.91,0:40:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 你在哪儿?\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.19,0:40:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二楼大厅 北扶梯口\N{\r原文字幕}Second floor rotunda, top of the north escalator.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.67,0:40:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?\N{\r原文字幕}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.43,0:40:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到北门入口了\N{\r原文字幕}We're coming into the loading dock, north entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.81,0:40:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你看到他了吗?  -看到了\N{\r原文字幕}-Have you got a visual?  -Yeah, I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.71,0:40:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有人布置在哪儿?  -各个主要出入口\N{\r原文字幕}-Where have you placed your men?  -We posted at all the main entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.46,0:40:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 一分钟后见\N{\r原文字幕}Okay, good. We should be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.57,0:40:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\r原文字幕}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.14,0:40:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你的人在停车场各出入口待命\N{\r原文字幕}Have your men cover all the parking level exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.63,0:40:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们上!\N{\r原文字幕}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.70,0:40:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想引起任何骚乱\N{\r原文字幕}I don't want to cause any kind of commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.43,0:40:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂?  -反恐小组在这儿\N{\r原文字幕}-Yeah?  -CTU's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.46,0:40:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算对那孩子采取行动\N{\r原文字幕}They're about to move in on the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.28,0:40:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先别行动 很棘手\N{\r原文字幕}Just stand down. It's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.85,0:40:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我唯一的机会 我不能让男孩被抓走\N{\r原文字幕}This is my only chance. We can't let the kid get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.06,0:40:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-别 别 等一下  -我不能等 戈麦斯!\N{\r原文字幕}-No, no, wait.  -I can't wait. Gomez!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.77,0:40:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿等 我正大光明地去抓他\N{\r原文字幕}Wait here, I want to make a clean grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.48,0:40:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\r原文字幕}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.57,0:41:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔.\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.15,0:41:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?\N{\r原文字幕}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.75,0:41:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫托尼·阿尔梅达\N{\r原文字幕}My name's Tony Almeida.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.34,0:41:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是联邦探员 来帮你的\N{\r原文字幕}I'm a federal agent, but I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.05,0:41:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸说你病了 是真的\N{\r原文字幕}What your father told you about your being sick is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.75,0:41:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信你\N{\r原文字幕}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.20,0:41:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来 我证明给你看\N{\r原文字幕}You come with me, I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.71,0:42:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快让开! 行动!\N{\r原文字幕}Get out of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.30,0:42:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮可 他的颈部被击中了!\N{\r原文字幕}Nicole, he's been hit in the neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.07,0:42:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰米 给我对讲机\N{\r原文字幕}Jamie, give me your walkie-talkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.24,0:42:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的警官被击中了\N{\r原文字幕}We have an officer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.49,0:42:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔 辛格勒逃了 重复 凯尔 辛格勒逃了\N{\r原文字幕}Kyle Singer is not in custody. I repeat, Kyle Singer is not in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.81,0:42:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各出口注意警戒\N{\r原文字幕}Maintain cover on all exits.
